                  and <placeName key="place_105399">Stonham Aspal (Stonham Antegan)</placeName>, and the hamlet of <placeName key="place_105255">Crowfield (Croffeld)</placeName>. 
                  Dated at <placeName role="date" key="place_105238">Coddenham (Codenham)</placeName> the Friday next
                  after the feast of St. Martin, <origDate notBefore="1341-01-25" notAfter="1342-01-24">15 Ed. III</origDate>. 
                   
